description:
Clipomatic is a smart video editor that turns everything you say into live captions. All you have to do is hit the magical record button, speak clearly and your words will appear as stylish captions right on your recording. Enhance the video with one of the artistic filters and wow your friends!

Videos with live captions made both fast and fun:
- caption a video in 40 languages using just your voice: select the speech recognition language right in the app;
- choose from a variety of caption styles to match your vibe;
- record in Square or Full format & use your videos in any type of social media posts;
- give your video a beautiful touch with one of the filters from our rich collection;
- captions editing is easy: just tap your caption to change the text;
- send your masterpieces directly to your Instagram and Facebook, or save to Camera Roll.

Make your content shine bright like a diamond, when:
- shooting stories on Instagram or other social media platforms - attract the attention of your followers easily when the sound is not played automatically;
- creating short travel videos, vlogs, how-to tutorials or DIY videos;
- making New Year’s resolutions or recording holiday greetings;
- saying “Hi” to your followers and wowing them with amazing videos;
- capturing another fabulous moment of your life.

Speech recognition is supported for the following languages:
Catalan, Chinese (Cantonese), Chinese (Mandarin), Chinese (Taiwan), Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch (The Netherlands), English (Australian), English (Canada), English (India), English (UK), English (US), Finnish, French, French (Canada), German, Greek, Hungarian, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Malay, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese, Portuguese (Brazil), Romanian, Russian, Slovak, Spanish, Spanish (Mexican), Swedish, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Vietnamese. 

Use hashtag #clipomatic for social media posts to share your creations with the community and follow us on Instagram at @clipomatic to view the most catchy ones!

Forget about a bunch of complicated video tools, Clipomatic is here for you to turn every moment into impressive memories with ease! Start making your awesome videos right now!

